    {
        "sha": "9c072e6462afe85e1764c35ed6bb593b8da6aa87",
        "author": "Bobby Chan",
        "email": "bobby.chan@sparkfun.com",
        "date": "2020-02-12T19:40:16Z",
        "message": "Update Old Pro Micro Examples\n\n- adjust the output for the hardware UART in **Blinkies.ino** file to distinguish betweeh the serial monitor\n- add `Keyboard.begin()` in `setup()` for **SimpleKeyboard_HID.ino**  (this appears to work without initializing it but it was added to be consistent with Arduino's reference example)\n- add `Mouse.begin()` in `setup()` to **SimpleJoystickMouse_HID.ino** (this appears to work without initializing it but it was added to be consistent with Arduino's reference example)\n- include the ability to invert the mouse using the joystick depending on the orientation of the joystick\n-autoformat",
        "url": "https://github.com/sparkfun/Pro_Micro/commit/9c072e6462afe85e1764c35ed6bb593b8da6aa87"
    },
    {
        "sha": "c61b946a1345b4ea0e32041608541068ea1110fd",
