        "url": "https://github.com/sparkfun/Pro_Micro/commit/c61b946a1345b4ea0e32041608541068ea1110fd"
    },
    {
        "sha": "65125df07256383dc092372c216a542befc24159",
        "author": "Bobby Chan",
        "email": "bobby.chan@sparkfun.com",
        "date": "2020-02-12T19:02:25Z",
        "message": "Update Pro Micro Examples\n\n- rename files to match the examples in the tutorial\n- adjust the output for the hardware UART in **Example_1_Blinkies_Hello.ino** file to distinguish betweeh the serial monitor\n- add `Keyboard.begin()` in `setup()` for **Example_2a_SimpleKeyboard_HID.ino**  (this appears to work without initializing it but it was added to be consistent with Arduino's reference example)\n- add `Mouse.begin()` in `setup()` to **Example_2b_SimpleJoystickMouse_HID.ino** (this appears to work without initializing it but it was added to be consistent with Arduino's reference example)\n- include the ability to invert the mouse using the joystick depending on the orientation of the joystick\n- include examples to that utilize Qwiic connect system using the Qwiic Joystick and Qwiic Keyboard\n- autoformat",
        "url": "https://github.com/sparkfun/Pro_Micro/commit/65125df07256383dc092372c216a542befc24159"
    },
